snippet.title: Little Nemo and the Guardians of Slumberland Kickstarter Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Explore a dream world as Little Nemo, armed with toys, candy, and stuffed animals in this colorful platforming metroidvania adventure. Back the Kickstarter campaign here: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/diesoft/little-nemo
